verbose_text: Mycoplasma pneumoniae pneumonia (MPP), a common acute respiratory tract infectious disease in children that has a variety of clinical manifestations, is caused by Mycoplasma pneumoniae (MP) infection, and can lead to multi-organ and multi-system damage.
